-- Housing Minister Says China to Keep Property Curbs, Business News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-19T02:08:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/china-to-keep-restrictions-for-property-market-china-business-news-says.html

          
          
             China will not relax curbs to cool
the property market, the China Business News reported on its Web
site today, citing Jiang Weixin, Minister of Housing and Urban-
Rural Construction.  
 Jiang made the comment at a confenrence on July 17,
according to the Shanghai-based newspaper.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Jian Guo Jiang in Shanghai at 
 jjiang@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        